title: Liquid or debris error message coming from last one week. Tried with different cables and cleaned.
content:
Constantly getting a "liquid or debris in charging port. Cannot charge"

Message despite trying multiple cables, cleaning phone etc. 

Happening since 2 weeks now and only able to charge phone when it is switching off. 

This is quite annoying and none of my phones before did this. Looks like over solutioning.
